# ── Secrets — NEVER commit values into these ────────────────────────────────
# The top-level .env IS tracked — but only ever with empty/placeholder values.
# Real values live in the developer's local copy; use:
#   git update-index --skip-worktree .env
# after pulling, so local secret edits never get committed.
*.env
.env.*
.env.bak
supabase/.temp/